attributes.title: Constant crashing and freezing
attributes.review: I downloaded this app to support the re-election of President Trump but whenever I logged on it would crash. attributes.title: Terrible
attributes.review: This app asks me to input my phone number before even gaining access to its features. I would never want to see anything regarding this app in my mailbox, voicemail, or recent texts. So I don’t understand why a phone number or any form of contact is necessary, it should be optional. 0/10. Terrible. Would not recommend. Ever. 🖐😒
